{"tid":456200,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解請假要問點解","createTime":"2017-11-02T18:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T10:36:52.000Z","uid":154997,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"07c1833e29588782b93ccea47a606027dcf06d25","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n你理得我姐？<br />\n你知道左唔通又可以唔批咩<br />\n你知道左咪棧自己條氣唔順<br />\n有時淨係想攞日假抖下 都唔知點講"},{"pid":"40b4f7553232bd83926667195a33d3b204d4089b","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"點解要負皮我<br />\n真心想知<br />\n定係負皮就係嗰d請親假都要問點解既嫁唔出既肥西女上司？<br />\n係呀 我請一日假係屋企溫仔其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55b531d737ab593ec2e2980c7870e7cfc517af6","tid":456200,"uid":152047,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要負皮我<br />\n真心想知<br />\n定係負皮就係嗰d請親假都要問點解既嫁唔出既肥西女上司？<br />\n係呀 我請一日假係屋企溫仔其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解負皮要問點解<br />\n你理得我姐？<br />\n你知道左唔通又可以唔畀咩<br />\n你知道左咪棧自己條氣唔順<br />\n有時淨係想俾負皮你個廢青 都唔知點講"},{"pid":"89462fc2cac10d7850e28ee3e24d8d9674eff146","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事請假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事返唔到工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁方便講"},{"pid":"70002e2bddb9ea0054ce49576d92c65b33f7aa07","tid":456200,"uid":130342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:41:00.000Z","msg":"點解你要知佢點解要問點解<br />\n你知左佢就唔會問你咩<br />\n咪又係要翻"},{"pid":"41f7a014a30a4d034ae7392d95ca6918b54ac8df","tid":456200,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:42:27.000Z","msg":"答佢抖吓"},{"pid":"8f602ae2bef0a5c30de287c76b2233dbce6da304","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你要知佢點解要問點解<br />\n你知左佢就唔會問你咩<br />\n咪又係要翻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係覺得好奇怪<br />\n明明私事請假<br />\n冇必要作為公事交代"},{"pid":"ad43230c841e06914130687ed08b01e08472bca4","tid":456200,"uid":145345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:45:02.000Z","msg":"我都覺<br />\n<br />\n但我個袋有好多理由耍走佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e6713e700d17003393bdf57266dfd5c71ca420","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>答佢抖吓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抖下？你唔返工人地做埋你嗰份呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （心諗: 你放假人地都要做埋你嗰份啦)<br />\n<br />\nBtw我份工係計鐘 返幾多得幾多"},{"pid":"b04141bd9d44216033c79db0e995523bd9e43e7c","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺<br />\n<br />\n但我個袋有好多理由耍走佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試舉例說明之"},{"pid":"c5940411a26ad6808cd3162e0a4a819921d69397","tid":456200,"uid":145345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都覺<br />\n<br />\n但我個袋有好多理由耍走佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試舉例說明之</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喂唔好啦掛 <br />\n屋企系列<br />\n自身系列<br />\n慢慢演繹啦<br />\n講晒出來我咪無貨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ef29763960ffb394ae68fbbe37df0b51fbf0ca","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都覺<br />\n<br />\n但我個袋有好多理由耍走佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試舉例說明之</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喂唔好啦掛 <br />\n屋企系列<br />\n自身系列<br />\n慢慢演繹啦<br />\n講晒出來我咪無貨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實假就一定請到 拎no pay<br />\n但每次諗起個肥西女上司問點解<br />\n請假好似要睇佢面色 求佢咁<br />\n就覺得好大壓力<br />\n佢會話 公司唔夠人 (冇一日夠人 長期缺人)<br />\n但係公司唔請夠人 唔撚係我責任"},{"pid":"9043e7d8dd879f28f4dcc1cbb88e168855f14d7d","tid":456200,"uid":155949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事請假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事返唔到工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁方便講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n辭職問點解 仲白痴啦<br />\n決定左走 就已經諗好曬<br />\n講咩都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acbfcabdb3182bcb2da2b07f54fb2b5daf8da71","tid":456200,"uid":38688,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事請假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事返唔到工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁方便講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n辭職問點解 仲白痴啦<br />\n決定左走 就已經諗好曬<br />\n講咩都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把人為錢走為錢留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa288d28b6751568d28758bc2feb7fd47433877","tid":456200,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T00:32:36.000Z","msg":"未試過俾人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416000c3aee4fb68488d866743e9c66cc8a6e910","tid":456200,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T00:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事請假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事返唔到工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁方便講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n辭職問點解 仲白痴啦<br />\n決定左走 就已經諗好曬<br />\n講咩都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把人為錢走為錢留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留左通常無好日子過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8036604d19c7507ee61f3d661de37ef2f34e62c","tid":456200,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"因為唔重視私穩<br />\n同埋搵理由拒絕你<br />\n<br />\n但明明我有假關你撚事<br />\n我係多野做請假<br />\n少野做返工呀吹呀"},{"pid":"7221cdfeff789d32389f70e8b4348c2ae94dc3b2","tid":456200,"uid":25619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"答佢去見工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4105a3f32bcd8dcc890fa6a9f1a23da9527a184b","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為唔重視私穩<br />\n同埋搵理由拒絕你<br />\n<br />\n但明明我有假關你撚事<br />\n我係多野做請假<br />\n少野做返工呀吹呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger<br />\n私隱中point"},{"pid":"a919393f57b8587ff19ca452e57fcf66a934fb2f","tid":456200,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:40:47.000Z","msg":"跟著好老細 話走就走 <br />\n直接通知老闆就可以走 我真係覺得自己好撚幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我老細仲hea過我"},{"pid":"27d6cefd7c12b11ebe5b0fbf8a473982176e6a63","tid":456200,"uid":24665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟著好老細 話走就走 <br />\n直接通知老闆就可以走 我真係覺得自己好撚幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我老細仲hea過我</blockquote><br />\n正路唔係老細都係好hea架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8223b0e56ff431d98d4d2716bf772f12d5da394f","tid":456200,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跟著好老細 話走就走 <br />\n直接通知老闆就可以走 我真係覺得自己好撚幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我老細仲hea過我</blockquote><br />\n正路唔係老細都係好hea架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係director都忙架 佢飛來飛去<br />\n佢一飛我就唔使翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2aea29e2f1c2fcce5f1ef600b236dae0e6bfc0","tid":456200,"uid":154997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩又問我點解要早走<br />\n唔通同你講去睇演唱會咩on99<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企有事唔方便講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他同事問起我要交代<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (仆街... 點9吹好) <br />\n<br />\n其實關其他人咩事<br />\n其實我計鐘出糧 我早走你都冇蝕底<br />\n問問問好閪煩<br />\n<br />\n我真係好想同佢講：個個都返工<br />\n唔通個個都想返工咩"},{"pid":"5e817167407d0ee01d3b4bb69414ee4b1ebf9c13","tid":456200,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:49:27.000Z","msg":"所以我請假原因寫返請假，照批"},{"pid":"a3782e31c226024ec74131adc1739b2c201a2ff9","tid":456200,"uid":155009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:36:52.000Z","msg":"吾好答囉！咁炒你唔會問點解"}]}